#. module: theme_bewise
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bewise.s_quotes_carousel_minimal
msgid ""
"\" A leading institution for growth. <br/>Supportive, forward-thinking, and "
"academically rigorous. \""
msgstr ""
"\" ສະຖາບັນຊັ້ນນໍາເພື່ອການເຕີບໂຕ. <br/>ໃຫ້ການສະໜັບສະໜູນ, ມີວິໄສທັດກວ້າງໄກ, ແລະ "
"ມີຄວາມເຂັ້ມງວດທາງດ້ານວິຊາການ. \""

#. module: theme_bewise
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bewise.s_quotes_carousel_minimal
msgid ""
"\" Outstanding education and support! <br/>They consistently exceed my "
"expectations. \""
msgstr ""
"\" ການສຶກສາ ແລະ ການສະໜັບສະໜູນທີ່ດີເລີດ! <br/>ພວກເຂົາເຮັດໄດ້ດີເກີນຄວາມຄາດໝາຍຂອງຂ້ອຍສະເໝີ. \""

#. module: theme_bewise
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bewise.s_quotes_carousel_minimal
msgid ""
"\" Their programs transformed my career. Innovative, challenging, and "
"inspiring. \""
msgstr ""
"\" ຫຼັກສູດຂອງພວກເຂົາໄດ້ປ່ຽນແປງອາຊີບຂອງຂ້ອຍ. ມີນະວັດຕະກໍາ, ທ້າທາຍ, ແລະ ສ້າງແຮງບັນດານໃຈ. \""

