#. module: theme_bewise
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bewise.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid ""
"A variety of pencils and pens provided for writing assignments, note-taking, "
"and completing tests and quizzes."
msgstr ""
"ມີສໍ ແລະ ບິກຫຼາກຫຼາຍຊະນິດທີ່ຈັດກຽມໄວ້ໃຫ້ສໍາລັບການຂຽນບົດຝຶກຫັດ, ການຈົດບັນທຶກ, ແລະ ການເຮັດບົດສອບເສັງ."

#. module: theme_bewise
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bewise.s_key_images
msgid "A vibrant community of thinkers and innovators"
msgstr "ສັງຄົມແຫ່ງນັກຄິດ ແລະ ນັກສ້າງສັນທີ່ເຕັມໄປດ້ວຍພະລັງ"

#. module: theme_bewise
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bewise.s_quadrant
msgid "Academic Excellence"
msgstr "ຄວາມເປັນເລີດທາງດ້ານວິຊາການ"

#. module: theme_bewise
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bewise.s_empowerment
msgid "Achieve with<br/>Summit University"
msgstr "ບັນລຸຜົນສໍາເລັດກັບ<br/>ມະຫາວິທະຍາໄລ Summit"

#. module: theme_bewise
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bewise.s_cards_grid
msgid "Advanced Learning Programs"
msgstr "ຫຼັກສູດການຮຽນຮູ້ຂັ້ນສູງ"

#. module: theme_bewise
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bewise.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid ""
"Advanced scientific calculators for math and science courses, helping "
"students perform complex calculations with ease."
msgstr ""
"ຈັກຄິດໄລ່ທາງວິທະຍາສາດຂັ້ນສູງສໍາລັບວິຊາຄະນິດສາດ ແລະ ວິທະຍາສາດ, "
"ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ນັກສຶກສາຄິດໄລ່ເລກທີ່ຊັບຊ້ອນໄດ້ຢ່າງງ່າຍດາຍ."

#. module: theme_bewise
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bewise.s_company_team_detail
msgid ""
"Alexander Rivera is an economics professor focused on macroeconomic theory "
"and international finance."
msgstr ""
"Alexander Rivera ແມ່ນອາຈານສອນເສດຖະສາດ ທີ່ເນັ້ນໃສ່ທິດສະດີເສດຖະສາດມະຫາພາກ ແລະ "
"ການເງິນລະຫວ່າງປະເທດ."

#. module: theme_bewise
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bewise.s_image_text
msgid "All students benefit from individualised support."
